Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • Team

  • class Team
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is name Team which contains information on a team name that something or some people created. The team contains four members and the class holds the names of all four members. Finally the class contains two object of the competition that the Team will participate in and will show the results of that competition.
    Since:
    22 March 2016
    Author:
    Brandon Hathaway
